      <body>
         <div xml:lang="xno">
            <p n="a#1" xml:space="preserve">Th<ex>et</ex> beke<ex>n</ex>nis ek <persName>Jon Olafson</persName> raadhma<ex>n</ex> i
        <persName>Berghwin</persName> m<ex>et</ex> thætta mit opeth breff at ek haffu<ex>er</ex>
      kærligha wnt / oc stadffæst the gaaffwo som h<ex>er</ex>ra <persName>Lifferdh</persName> min
      fadhir brodh<ex>e</ex>r gudh hans siæll haffue gaff till <placeName>hælgandz / husit
        /</placeName> i <placeName>Aalburgh</placeName> som ær grund oc jordh som oss badhom till
      hørdhe oc ligghir i <placeName>sancte Botolfs sokn</placeName> wpa norra gatu<ex>n</ex>ne millo<ex>m</ex>
      <placeName>s<ex>anc</ex>ta G<ex>er</ex>trudha jordh</placeName> oc thæn jordh som
        <persName>Johanna Libbert</persName>s wpa bodhe tha ha<ex>n</ex> th<ex>et</ex> gaff fra mik
      oc mina arfwa oc till forne<ex>m</ex>pnt <placeName>hælgandz hws</placeName> till
      æu<ex>er</ex>dheligh ægho . ♦</p>
            <p n="a#2" xml:space="preserve">Oc thy forbiudh<ex>e</ex>r iak <persName>Kristine Olafsdott<ex>er</ex></persName> oc alla
      andra thær nakat mote tala æll<ex>e</ex>r hindra thæssa gaaffuo i nakra handa matto .
      ♦</p>
            <p n="a#3" xml:space="preserve">Oc till sanni<ex>n</ex>da oc mer<ex>e</ex> wisso h<ex>e</ex>r wm tha bedhis iak biskedhelikæ
      ma<ex>n</ex>na incighle som ær <persName>Nisse Magn<ex>us</ex>s<ex>on</ex></persName> oc
        <persName>Gutthorm Jonss<ex>on</ex></persName> raadhme<ex>n</ex> i
        <placeName>Berghui<ex>n</ex></placeName> m<ex>eth</ex> mino incighle for<ex>e</ex> thætta
      breff ♦ som skriffuit war j <placeName>Berghwin</placeName> thiisdaghin næsta
      ffor<ex>e</ex> sancta Marg<ex>r</ex>eto dagh anno domini m<hi rend="sup">o</hi>cd<hi rend="sup">o</hi>xxx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> septimo . ♦</p>
         </div>
